Carnatron hit the ground and his gun was jarred from his grap and he made a 
cry when his body slammed against the ground. Carnatron as he was tackled 
instinctivly sent out tons of black spikes straight our from his body...if 
this was the suit or himself he wasnt sure but they went about 6 feet 
out. "Eat this!" he yelled at Rodimus telpathicly. He then looked over 
Rodimus's shoulder and saw Hydras barring down on Rodimus with swords slicing 
down on him left to right, not meant to impale but give a deep gash.
